{"tid":2445594,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"十歲係咪人生轉捩點","createTime":"2021-03-13T17:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T04:20:53.000Z","uid":30836,"like":12,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c7778233857a201f8009c707f330c1e0decdc825","tid":2445594,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T17:40:44.000Z","msg":"轉眼間就差唔多小學畢業 成10歲人<br />\n生活、學孽、家庭　要背負嘅嘢都愈嚟愈大<br />\n<br />\n有時認真照下鏡　好容易發現到歲月既痕跡<br />\n<br />\n講係咁講 但總係覺得自己好似長唔大咁<br />\n10歲既驅殼入面 依然係幼稚園嘅靈魂<br />\n<br />\n回望返剛畢業後自己想讀嘅academia path 想做既科長<br />\n完全唔係自己而家做緊嘅嘢<br />\n但已經返唔到轉頭　 只能夠繼續見步行步<br />\n或者喺香港　呢啲係好多人都必須做嘅妥協<br />\n<br />\n1999<br />\n其實今日開學日 只係想乞句學業進步"},{"pid":"7ffe52b6f4e3a049f067432456e98a6ce15359d8","tid":2445594,"uid":387826,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T17:41:59.000Z","msg":"係呀 <br />\n訓啦<br />\n柒頭"},{"pid":"a920e2357fbcd04ae38aaf9356a11fb0ae522d05","tid":2445594,"uid":80493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T18:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f6950d2dad5b65921efd928e61408093fe0d76","tid":2445594,"uid":200321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T19:30:54.000Z","msg":"係啊55555"},{"pid":"8619da6c5e2b2fe74a9f95e8649f18c11f29df4e","tid":2445594,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T19:33:47.000Z","msg":"五碎 十五碎 二十碎呢"},{"pid":"12c57f30dc83afd42cdce1b99cad648a815c18da","tid":2445594,"uid":224190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T19:55:48.000Z","msg":"三十碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a28f6ee4b37dad3e77fe9ef673db9fedec0811","tid":2445594,"uid":58201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T01:24:41.000Z","msg":"係 樓豬加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc0e269991fade5539d693cbd6653bda7168698","tid":2445594,"uid":36739,"li